    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brush strokes found in traditional Chinese painting.  Associated with the Northern Song dynasty painter Guo Xi (active 1068-1078), these curved strokes resemble gathering clouds.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
